sources.title: Psychoanalysis (Free Full Movie) Drama Suspense
sources.description:
Paul Symmonds is the country's top suicide prevention psychologist... Then five of his clients commit suicide in a one week period. He's suspended from practicing and forced to undergo a psychological evaluation. Then Paul begins to suspect the psych in charge of his evaluation actually murdered his clients in order to take the top spot for himself.

Directed by James Raue
2015
Starring  Benedict Wall, Ryan O'Kane, Michael Whalley
